@rlevas @aajisaka It looks like this commit broke a couple of Kerberos-related unit tests on trunk, see [post-commit build](https://builds.apache.org/job/Ambari-trunk-Commit/8620/).  I see that the PR-builder said that test passed, but following [the link](https://builds.apache.org/job/Ambari-Github-PullRequest-Builder/203/) reveals that it built the wrong commit.  I think this problem with the PR builder was addressed by @vivekratnavel since then.

```
 > git checkout -f 881b464983d84b795737413e137922dca6c3f06f
Commit message: "AMBARI-22788 Unsightly artifacts during Login. (atkach)"
```
